<body>
    <h1>Returns Policy</h1>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Return Policy for Perishable Items</h2>
        <p>Due to the perishable nature of seafood, we do not accept product returns once they have been delivered.</p>
        <p>However, we are committed to ensuring your complete satisfaction with your purchase.</p>
        
        <div class="important-note">
            <strong>Important:</strong> Please inspect your order immediately upon delivery to verify the quality and correctness of the items.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Quality Guarantee</h2>
        <p>All our products come with a freshness and quality guarantee. If you receive a product that doesn't meet our quality standards, you may be eligible for a refund or replacement.</p>
        <p>Our quality standards include:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Proper temperature maintenance</li>
            <li>Fresh appearance and smell</li>
            <li>Intact packaging</li>
            <li>Correct items as per your order</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Damaged or Incorrect Items</h2>
        <p>If your order arrives damaged, spoiled, or is incorrect, please follow these steps:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Contact us within 2 hours of delivery</li>
            <li>Email us at support@finefish.com or call +977-9801234567</li>
            <li>Include your order number and a clear description of the issue</li>
            <li>Provide clear photographs showing the problem with the product</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Our customer service team will review your case promptly and guide you through the next steps.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Refund Process</h2>
        <p>Once we validate your complaint, we will process your refund or replacement as follows:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>For valid quality or delivery issues, we offer a full refund or replacement (your choice)</li>
            <li>Refunds will be processed within 3 business days</li>
            <li>The refund will be issued using the original payment method</li>
            <li>For replacements, we will schedule a new delivery at the earliest possible time</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Cancellation Policy</h2>
        <p>Orders can be cancelled before they are dispatched:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Log into your account and cancel from your order history</li>
            <li>Call our customer service at +977-9801234567</li>
            <li>Once an order is dispatched, it cannot be cancelled</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-info">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about our returns policy, please don't hesitate to contact us:</p>
        <p>
            <strong>Email:</strong> support@finefish.com<br>
            <strong>Phone:</strong> +977-9801234567<br>
            <strong>Hours:</strong> Monday-Saturday, 7:00 AM - 6:00 PM
        </p>
